ote>個中字如果解作合意時要讀第三聲zung3/jung3。<br />\n好似<br />\n睇中(zung3/jung3)<br />\n中(zung3/jung3)獎<br />\n正中(zung3/jung3)下懷<br />\n<br />\n中字喺解位置先會讀第一聲zung1/jung1。<br />\n好似<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)間<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)學<br />\n萬中(zung1/jung1)無一<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n係有中意呢個詞語，但並唔係而家一般所講嘅鍾意。而且讀音根本唔同。<br />\n中(zung3/jung3)意就係字面解合自己嘅心意。<br />\n鍾(zung1/jung1)意就係鍾愛嘅心意。<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)意就係中間嘅心意。係咩嚟？</blockquote><br />\nquote下source好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae1d0eb8b4a13df700d67ca3f9f0d9600a2f427","tid":332513,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>舖排黎， 遲下就可以將台灣啲總統、行政院長全部加返引號，學返大陸</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真係好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家啲中史書已經加晒引號<br />\n「總統」、 前「總統」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊間出版社咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165cc2d1dd94929995c4504b86cc072378d10154","tid":332513,"uid":99331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>舖排黎， 遲下就可以將台灣啲總統、行政院長全部加返引號，學返大陸</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真係好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家啲中史書已經加晒引號<br />\n「總統」、 前「總統」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊間出版社咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇記錯係香港教圖<br />\n一教到近代就係咁幫台灣嘅嘢加引號"},{"pid":"866a0ff51546d1aa7b26485cb0cb4a1ca8c